text: José Panizo (5 October 1936 - 24 November 2018) was a Spanish wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Spanish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Spain Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Madrid
